OL,6,F"They must use the University's #188m
OL,7,Fof available cash to fund a more
OL,8,Fcautious and evidence-based approach
OL,9,Fto improving our finances without
OL,10,Fdestroying our members' lives."
OL,12,FThe decision by union members now
OL,13,Fmeans staff could go ahead with
OL,14,Findustrial action unless compulsory
OL,15,Fredundancies are ruled out by the
OL,16,Funiversity.
